com.xaguzman.artemiscommons.components.collidershapes

Class CircleCollider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xaguzman.artemiscommons.components.collidershapes.ColliderShape
      • com.xaguzman.artemiscommons.components.collidershapes.CircleCollider

  • public class CircleCollider
extends ColliderShape
    Collider with circle shape, where it's xy is absolute (world xy). It has a radius, and the middle of the radius is given by left and bottom properties. Created by gdlxguzm on 3/28/2017.
